➜园所升级！上海新增市一级幼儿园公示名单出炉！民办就有4所
http://www.sohu.com/a/421079002_172239	56292
<p class="ql-align-center">最新消息！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上海又有<strong>19</strong>所幼儿园</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">升级成一级园啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200926/7990229c5e2446aca30b362b6f61bebf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">全市各区新增<strong>19所</strong>“市一级幼儿园”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是近几年评级中新增民办园最多的一次，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">新增一级园最多的是青浦区！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/7c2d0c66584f408d8a0e977a21181fb1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上海市每年年中、年末两次一级园验收</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">评分规则很严格，创建更多优质幼儿园</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个“市级一级幼儿园”的称号不简单！</p>
