<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>康宁科技实验小学</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">录取条件：2020，居住证+积分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200926/9b30e8d4c9384470aa8a607a7fc40052.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
