http://www.sohu.com/a/421081476_172239	57776
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200927/6472968618a84a33beb540599203ccdb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">入学君最近在裙里发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">家长们对<strong>统筹</strong>不太了解</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经常会问：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">统筹是什么？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">统筹靠运气吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200927/dfe1f7df0b3b4931b82d6794b33c2815.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
